# Dedicated coverage for the WebSocket sampler/streamer comps + the halstreamer /
# halsampler clients: a streamer feeds values received over a WebSocket onto HAL
# pins, wired straight into a sampler that transmits them back over a WebSocket to
# halsampler.  A loopback of all four pin types, driven from the shell clients.
loadrt streamer cfg=fbus depth=100
loadrt sampler  cfg=fbus depth=100
net p0 streamer.pin.0 => sampler.pin.0
net p1 streamer.pin.1 => sampler.pin.1
net p2 streamer.pin.2 => sampler.pin.2
net p3 streamer.pin.3 => sampler.pin.3
newthread fast 1000000
addf streamer fast
addf sampler fast
